name: Wake N Bake - Verbal Assault *Preorder*
description: Wake N Bake has spent all year perfecting Verbal Assault and its finally nearing its completion. With a small handful of songs to record before sending it in to be mastered we have decided its time to start taking orders. This album features hooks from Dubbs, Crytic Wisdom, Mark A, and more. All pre-orders include a free 11"x17" Jester Poster, and will ship within 48 hours of the hard copies arriving at Dead Broke Entertainment. The final track is scheduled to be recorded during the first week of June. Tracks: 19 Runtime: Approx 1:15:00 7 Track Pre-Release EP | "Pick Your Price" Download, Free Allowed!

name: Logo Pendants *PREORDER*
description:
Official Dead Broke Logo Pendants are now open to pre-order.  Each pendant ships with a free copy of Wake N Bake's new album Verbal Assault and an 11" x 17" Jester Poster.  These pendants are made from high quality Stainless Steel and come in two different finishes, brushed and high polish.  The brushed metal shows less wear and tear on the long haul and is easier to maintain.  The high polish finish is ideal for people who want their pendant to shine, but are sick of micropave.   Either piece will last years and wont fade to an unsightly base metal within a few months.

Measurements: TBA (2.5" - 3" Wide)
Material: Stainless Steel
Finish Choices: Brushed, High Polish

name: 11" x 17" Jester Poster
description:
The Jester, a classic sign of a public entertainer, laid bare and reduced to an angry skull throwing up dual middle fingers with the Dead Broke Family amassed behind him.  Includes the Dead Broke Entertainment "Slant Text" logo on the bottom and lists the roster at time of printing across the top.  

Dimensions 11" x 17". 

Limited Edition. Only 100 posters with this design will be pressed.  
Printed on high-gloss 100 lb. text stock with aqueous coating.  Designed by Wake N Bake.

name: Limited Edition Skull & Wings / Logo Shirt
description:
Printed on Gildan Heavy Cotton Preshrunk T-Shirts.  Limited Edition Artwork, only 50 units were made, and no more are going to be produced.  The front features a Skull with red highlights, and a banner that says "Dead Broke" beneath it.  The back of the shirt has the Official Dead Broke Entertainment logo printed between the shoulder blades.  These shirts were printed using industry standard Silk Screening processes that last wash after wash without fading.  Sizes available: L - 3XL.  Some sizes may be sold out.

Front Print Dimensions: 13" Wide
Back Print Dimensions: 7" Wide
Image Placement: 2.5" Below the bottom of the collar
